title: Conquering Dystopia (Official Guitar Transcription)
description:
Description:

"The Complete Guitar Transcription for Conquering Dystopia's Self Titled 2014 album.

We all know that Jeff Loomis and Keith Merrow are finger-gymnists - but something special occurs when they come together and combine their talents. The result is Conquering Dystopia's debut album. Now that it has been transcribed, it has become our largest selection of music notes in a single book!
That's not surprising if you are familiar with the record though - it's full of colourful scales, chord shapes, and solos. Pretty much from start to finish!
We hope you enjoy Keith and Jeff's all encompassing approach to the fretboard and implement an idea or two into your own playing.
Good luck, because you are going to need it to get this stuff up to speed!

Tunings:
A E A D G B E - All Songs"



Notices:

1. This download includes ONLY the official Guitar Pro files. You'll need Guitar Pro 6 or a newer version to open the .gpx files.
2. PLEASE SEED! Other people may want this content as bad as you, so make sure to seed at least at 1:1.
3. Make sure to support the musicians you love by buying their content if you can!
